queries.response: SJSU offers the following engineering programs: Biological Systems Engineering, Biomedical Engineering, Civil Engineering, Computer Engineering, Computer Science, Construction Management, Electrical Engineering, Engineering Physics, Environmental Engineering, Industrial Engineering, Materials Science and Engineering, Mechanical Engineering, and Mechatronics Engineering.

queries.query: Tell me about campus health services.
queries.response: Student Health Services (SHS) offers services such as medical exams, vaccinations, and health counseling. They also provide health education programs and workshops on topics such as stress management and nutrition. SHS is located in the Student Health Center, 145 S 7th St, San Jose, CA 95192, and is open Monday-Friday, 8:00 AM-5:00 PM. Appointments can be made by calling 408-924-6120.
